{
  "stem": "24462.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the camps, in our-- in the-- this is DP camps, we had a Jewish organization and the Jewish distribution of food, which was the main concern of people, food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other concern was how to migrate somewhere, how to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But with Germans, who talked to Germans?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never met Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never talked to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the DP camps, what did you know about the numbers of the Jews that had been killed?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were shocked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was shocked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody was looking how to organize themselves, how to get out of it, how to go somewhere, how to start new life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the main thing in the camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We left the camps with-- with the Bricha.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From Germany, it was organized to go to Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from-- to Austria, we went by foot, on foot, crossing the border and the rivers and things like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from-- from Bad Reichenhall, in Germany, we went to a camp near the Italian border.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we crossed the Alps on foot with a group of maybe 200 people, children, older people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We crossed the Alps in July, in snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "WE can imagine how high was it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This climbing wasn't so hard like this descending.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't so hard, like-- to get off the mountain, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't-- because of the snow, because of the cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we came to a camp called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was Haganah camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was organized so that this was on the Italian side of the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the Italians had a agreement with the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because of the British intelligence interfering with this migration, they didn't want the Jews to come to Italy and go put the pressure on Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
